---
title: Indian Chickpea Coconut Curry with Garlic Flatbread Dippers & Yoghurt
description: Roasting an array of colourful veggies is an instant winner and a great way to boost any curry. Stir the veggies and the chickpeas through a tomato spiced curry sauce, mild and with notes of ginger, to allow everything to blend into one big bowl of deliciousness.
